posts.post_title: t207 group sold - A few left for individual sale incl. Peters & Kuhn (Broadleaf backs)
posts.post_content:
Posted By: Brian McQueen

The bulk of the t207s have sold but I do have a few left for individual sale.  The two keys of that group are two of the cards remaining below - Kuhn and Peters.  Prices include shipping and insurance and scans are available upon request.  Thanks in advance,

Brian


Fromme VG - mostly sharp corners, no wrinkling -- $40
Gainor VG/EX - mostly sharp corners, no wrinkling -- 45
Henrickson VG - mild corner wear, no wrinkling -- $35
Kuhn PR - left/right borders trimmed...surface scrapes on front, back damage...lowest pop reports in set!! [BROADLEAF BACK] -- $125
Lively EX - mostly sharp corners, no wrinkling -- $50
Milan FR- tiny nick in side, faint wrinkle - $20
Peters SGC 30 - offcentered but little wear and no wrinkling [BROADLEAF BACK] -- $225
Schaefer VG - offcentered, sharp corners, no wrinkling -- $35
